		<img class="lconnSprite lconnSprite-iconAttention16" src="../../../resources/web/com.ibm.lconn.core.styles.oneui3/images/blank.gif?etag=20150110.113307" alt="Information icon" /><span class="lotusAltText">Information icon</span><span name="message"></span>
